Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:02.57,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穏やかに暮らしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:08.48,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君となら出来るはず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.65,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや出来ないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.56,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも君と過ごせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:24.80,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それだけでいいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.58,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ピントが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.18,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ズレたような
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.26,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,２人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.07,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今もおんなじか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:58.30,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悪い奴を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.26,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黙らせに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:07.58,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:12.39,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繰り返していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.83,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無茶なことばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.16,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.01,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんなに悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.48,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:33.20,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穏やかに暮らしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:39.33,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君となら出来るはず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.16,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いや出来ないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:48.24,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だが僕の告白は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:55.51,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,実ること祈ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:03.48,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穏やかな風が吹く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:09.58,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの場所に帰れたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:15.48,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう思うけどもう誰か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:21.53,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待ってたか待ってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:24.64,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.40,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,また出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.64,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんを言う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.68,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,けど君を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.52,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.59,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.60,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わかるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:45.51,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この文字は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.91,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:20:02.57,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想过安稳的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:08.48,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的话应该能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.65,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.56,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要能和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:24.80,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.58,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.18,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.26,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像失焦了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.07,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:58.30,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:03.26,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:07.58,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:12.39,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:16.83,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.16,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.01,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也并非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:25.48,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太坏的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:33.20,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想过安稳的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:39.33,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的话应该能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.16,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可能不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:48.24,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过祈愿我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:55.51,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:03.48,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风平稳地吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:09.58,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经回到了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:15.48,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我已经记不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:21.53,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁曾经等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:24.64,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁仍在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:27.40,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.64,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.68,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.52,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.59,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.60,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:45.51,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段文字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.91,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是属于你的
